### Video and Image
> ðŸ§ª This module has just been migrated. If animations/effects/transitions donâ€™t take effect, please open an issue.

- â˜‘ï¸ Add local video/image media, and [customize segment timing, duration, or playback speed](#source-trimming-and-global-speed)
